Package: basen
Type: Package
Title: BASEN: Base-level Abundance estimation with Species-assigned Evidence using Nanopore
Version: 0.1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Heewon", "Seo", , "Heewon.Seo@ucalgary.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Calculate genome-size-normalized species-level relative abundance
    from Kraken2 .report and .kraken outputs using species-specific
    k-mer assignments and reference genome sizes.
